```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>School Class Schedule</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
        }
        table {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
        }
        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Upcoming Semester Class Schedule</h1>
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Course Name</th>
                <th>Instructor</th>
                <th>Time</th>
                <th>Room Number</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Introduction to Computer Science</td>
                <td>Dr. A. Sharma</td>
                <td>Mon, Wed, Fri 10:00 AM - 11:30 AM</td>
                <td>Room 101</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Mathematics for Engineers</td>
                <td>Prof. B. Gupta</td>
                <td>Tue, Thu 9:00 AM - 10:30 AM</td>
                <td>Room 102</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>English Literature</td>
                <td>Ms. C. Kapoor</td>
                <td>Mon, Wed 1:00 PM - 2:30 PM</td>
                <td>Room 103</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Physics I</td>
                <td>Dr. D. Kumar</td>
                <td>Tue, Thu 11:00 AM - 12:30 PM</td>
                <td>Room 104</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>History of Art</td>
                <td>Prof. E. Singh</td>
                <td>Fri 2:00 PM - 4:00 PM</td>
                <td>Room 105</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
```

This HTML page includes a visually appealing table for the school's class schedule, with columns for the course name, instructor, course time, and room number. The CSS styling enhances the readability of the table by adding a background color to headers and alternating row colors for better distinction.
